{"tid":237723,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人去印度旅行唔肯打防疫針，有咩方法說服佢地？","createTime":"2017-05-10T14:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T23:45:28.000Z","uid":45185,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0863cbe99c912bba17689f15dd27593a26379313","tid":237723,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"最近兩老班friend搵埋佢地去印度，<br />\n佢地見成世人未去過有假又想試吓，<br />\n咁我就同佢地講要打防疫針啦，<br />\n點知即刻起曬鋼發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地既藉口係跟團同住五星級酒店冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果刻我深深感受到咩叫食古不化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好似啲廢老唔撚鍾意做身體檢查咁話怕驗到有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (仲要私家做價錢唔撚係平)<br />\n佢地死佢地事啦，但係住埋同一間屋有事起嚟我都要含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩方法可以哄佢地去打齊啲針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次關乎到條命仔我真係笑唔撚出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9b74049b1f572f9dee1ed5301beaa8721ceee3","tid":237723,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"求救"},{"pid":"95631dd20c04f6d793ed7f2952e50ca6de4937a4","tid":237723,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"由得佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己打咗先 佢死佢地事"},{"pid":"dda1b44fe866f1eb4c789c40bfe3c4d8c4b4d80a","tid":237723,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由得佢死<img src=\"